Loops are used to iterate the task.
Example:
- name: Postfix is Running
  service:
    name: Postfix
    state: started
- name: Dovelet is Running
  service:
    name: Dovelet
    state: started

How to Check all services running using loops?

- name: Postfix & Dovelet is running
  service:
    name: "{{ item }}"
    state: started
  loop:
    - postfix:
    - dovelet:

How to Check all services running using loops and vars?
 Vars:
   mail_services:
       - postfix
       - dovelet
   tasks:
     - name: Postfix & Dovelet is running
       service:
         name: "{{ item }}"
         state: started
       loop: "{{mail_services}}"

How to create users using a loop
- name: create users using a loop
  hosts: all
  tasks:
  - name: create users
    user:
      name: "{{ item.name }}"
      state: present
      groups: "{{item.groups}}"
    loop:
      - name: anna
        groups: wheel
      - name: linda
        groups: users
      - name: bob
        groups: users


